init_text:
A woman has been dating guy after guy, but it never seems to work out. She’s unaware that she’s actually been dating the same guy over and over; a shapeshifter who’s fallen for her, and is certain he’s going to get it right this time.

One day,

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: she meets a man who’s everything she’s ever wanted.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She’s certain he’s the one, but she’s also certain she’s going to lose him.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She’s determined to not let that happen again.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She’s going to hold on to this one.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He was in a bar, and she was with her friends.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He was so handsome, and he was staring at her.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She was going to call him.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The two continued to date and the woman was so happy.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She had finally found the man she was looking for.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She had finally found the man she was looking for and he was a player.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She was so upset that she went to the bar and got drunk.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She was so upset that she didn't even notice the man who was sitting at the bar watching her.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The man was watching the woman and couldn't help but notice how upset she was.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He couldn't help but feel bad for her.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He wanted to go over and talk to her, but he didn't want to come off as a creep.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He wanted to help her feel better.
